MNUMBER 59
  ADJECTIVE 133
  NAME golem
  *DESCRIPTION_START
Before you stands an animated corpse, sewn together from several pieces. A dull red light glows faintly from far back inside its eyes.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  ARMOR 80
  ATTACK1 200
  BODY 500
  EXTRABODY 500
  DEFENSE 200
  GENDER 2
  HUMAN
  SPEED 4
  STRATEGY 600
  WEAPON 544 163 100
  WEAPONPLUS 30
  MAGICWEAPON 1
  IMMUNITY 0 0
  IMMUNITY 2 1
  IMMUNITY 3 0
  IMMUNITY 4 0
  IMMUNITY 5 0
  IMMUNITY 7 0
  IMMUNITY 6 1
  IMMUNITY 9 0
  RACE 28
  SKINADJ 586
  SKINITEM 527 100 100 0
  DISEASE 25 10
  RESIST 50
  SPECUSE 10
  SPECBASE 50
  SPECDMG 50
  SPECDMGTYPE CRUSH
  TEXX %s slams into %s with a massive fist!
  TEX1 A flesh golem moans softly.
  TEX2 Pieces of flesh drop off of the arm of a flesh golem.
  TEX3 A flesh golem swivels its head from side to side, surveying the area.
  TEX4 A flesh golem flexes its huge fingers.
