MNUMBER 99
  NAME flitterer
  ATTACK1 1
  BODY 10
  ETERNAL
  DEFENSE 1
  GENDER 2
  PART 1
  SPEED 3
  STRATEGY 2
  TREASURE 0
  *DESCRIPTION_START
You see a small golden creature, glowing with soft white light, which looks just like a disembodied set of butterfly wings, shimmering and colorful, whose irridescent shades cascade over its surface like tumbling water.
  *DESCRIPTION_END
  TEX1 A glowing flitterer dances about the room.
  TEX2 A flitterer lands briefly and flexes its wings.
  TEX3 A flitterer flies in circles, weaving complex patterns of light.
  TEX4 A flitterer hums its strange song loudly.
  TEXE A flitterer flutters in.
  TEXM A flitterer flutters
  TEXD A flitterer drops to the ground and slowly stops moving, its glow fading.
