  ARTICLE SOME
  IFPREVERB EAT -1
    IFVAR ITEMADJ3 = 1324
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You take a shrimp off the plate, dip it in the sauce and eat it, savoring the smooth, delicate taste of the meat. Being careful to get at all the good meat, you pull off the shell and discard it.
      ECHO OTHERS %N removes a shrimp off the plate, dips it in the sauce and eats it, removing and discarding the shell.
