      ECHO OTHERS %N gestures at %a.
      ECHO ALL The power of the spell is completely absorbed by %a!
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 SPELLNUM
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
      EQUAL CHASCLOAK DUMMY1
      MOD CHASCLOAK 10
      EQUAL ITEMVAL1 SKILL23
      DIV ITEMVAL1 10
      ADD ITEMVAL1 CHASCLOAK
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 0
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = SPELLNUM
      IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 1
