NUMBER 2447
NAME The Garden of Wonderment
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Strange and unearthly plants reach out from odd angles, grasping and groping and straining and tugging at your very being. Every nerve in your body wants to race and dance around, but your feet are like molasses, and your brain seems to be off meditating somewhere on the other side of the garden.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 2447
OUTOFBODY
IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Your brain is way too foggy to do that right now.
