  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Everything seems all wavy and out of focus... perhaps you did it wrong...
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SEARCH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You rummage around in the back of your thoughts, and discover a whole new world!
  MOVE 2448
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You hear a strange, distant keening sound, like the crying of a wounded insect, detached from its head and floating away on the breeze. It calls to you, beckoning you closer... closer... closer...
  MOVE 2449
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You catch a strong whiff of thoughts and notions and orange and flying time and a great sweaty hand, which reeks of grape juice and suddenly grabs you by the scruff of the back, yanking you away.
  MOVE 2450
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RECALL -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you try to recall something of this garden, one of the plants fixes itself in your thoughts. Taking root there, it begins to bloom, becoming a beautiful flower as it feeds on the soil of your mind.
  MOVE 2451
ENDIF
IFPREVERB FROWN -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You frown, full to overflowing brim of sadness, flavored with cream and sugar. Suddenly a vast yet invisible hand the color of awakening grasps the handle and takes a sip.
  MOVE 2446
ENDIF
