NUMBER 2450
NAME Floating and Spinning
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Though you are motionless, the entire rest of the universe floats and spins wildly all around you, so fast that everything becomes a blur. Every little motion of the air rebounds with a thud against your tender skin as colors cascade like falling water.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 2450
OUTOFBODY
IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Your brain is way too foggy to do that right now.
ENDIF
