  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Well, you think you cast it right... but nothing seems to happen...
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PROJECT -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Everything seems all wavy and out of focus... perhaps you did it wrong...
ENDIF
