  ECHO PLAYER You smell burnt almonds, combined with rotten eggs and sour milk, flying off on a grand adventure in a silver dirigible.
  MOVE 2446
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RECALL -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You suddenly recall that everything shouldn't be spinning nearly so hard.
  MOVE 2447
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SMILE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you smile, things stop moving round and round and start going up and down instead.
