        ECHO OTHERS %N chants softly over the table.
        EQUAL GOLEMSET 2
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFVAR CHASTABLE = 6
    IFVAR SPELLNUM = 503
      CLEARVERB
      EQUAL CHASTABLE 0
      ECHO PLAYER You call down the forces of nature in the form of a lightning bolt, which impacts with the corpse on the table, causing it to crackle with energy for a moment.
      ECHO OTHERS %N gestures, and a massive bolt of lightning falls from the sky into the rotting corpse on the table, which crackles with energy for a moment.
      PLREVENT 1
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL Suddenly, the corpse begins to stir!
      IFVAR GOLEMSET ! 2
